## How to Test
1.  Ensure your dev server is running (`npm run dev`).
2.  Open [http://localhost:5173/](http://localhost:5173/).
3.  Use the top floating selector to switch between the component library and the app prototype.
4.  Navigate through the mobile app tabs and try the light/dark mode toggle in Settings.
